# Laravel Telescope

- **Package**: [laravel/telescope](https://laravel.com/docs/12.x/telescope) v5. Debug dashboard at `/telescope` (local only; admin panel access).
- **Local-only**: Registered in `AppServiceProvider` when `APP_ENV=local`; `dont-discover` in composer.json.
- **Gate**: `viewTelescope` allows users who `can('access admin panel')` (same as Horizon).
- **Filter**: Local = all entries; non-local = exceptions, failed requests/jobs, scheduled tasks, slow queries, monitored tags.
- **Tagging**: Request entries tagged with `status:{code}`. Add tags to monitoring list for production debugging.
- **Avatar**: User avatars from Spatie Media Library `avatar` collection.
- **Pruning**: `telescope:prune` scheduled daily. Response cache excludes `telescope/*`.

Consider the **telescope** skill when configuring or debugging with Telescope.
